=========================================
THREAT ANALYSIS
=========================================

1. Insider Threat

Description:
Security risk caused by employees or authorized users.

Impact:
Data theft and unauthorized access.

Prevention:
Access control and employee monitoring.

------------------------------------------------

2. Malware

Description:
Malicious software designed to damage systems.

Impact:
Data loss and system compromise.

Prevention:
Antivirus software and regular updates.

------------------------------------------------

3. Phishing

Description:
Fake emails or websites used to steal information.

Impact:
Credential theft and financial loss.

Prevention:
Security awareness training.

------------------------------------------------

4. Weak Passwords

Description:
Easy-to-guess passwords.

Impact:
Unauthorized account access.

Prevention:
Strong password policies and MFA.

------------------------------------------------

5. Unpatched Systems

Description:
Systems missing security updates.

Impact:
Exploitation of known vulnerabilities.

Prevention:
Regular patch management.
